verses.verse: Michtam <S%H4387><s%> of <S%H1732>David.<s%> <S%H8104>Preserve<s%> me, O <S%H410>God:<s%> <S%H3588>for<s%> in thee do I put my <S%H2620>trust.<s%>
O my soul, thou hast <S%H559>said<s%> unto the <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> <S%H859>Thou<s%> art my <S%H136>Lord:<s%> my <S%H2896>goodness<s%> extendeth <S%H1077>not<s%> <S%H5921>to<s%> thee;
But to the <S%H6918>saints<s%> <S%H834>that<s%> are in the <S%H776>earth,<s%> and to the <S%H117>excellent,<s%> in whom is <S%H3605>all<s%> my <S%H2656>delight.<s%>

Their <S%H6094>sorrows<s%> shall be <S%H7235>multiplied<s%> that <S%H4116>hasten<s%> after <S%H312>another<s%> god: their drink <S%H5262>offerings<s%> of <S%H4480>blood<s%> <S%H1818><s%> will I <S%H1077>not<s%> <S%H5258>offer,<s%> <S%H1077>nor<s%> take <S%H5375>up<s%> <S%H853><s%> their <S%H8034>names<s%> <S%H5921>into<s%> my <S%H8193>lips.<s%>
The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> is the <S%H4521>portion<s%> of mine <S%H2506>inheritance<s%> and of my <S%H3563>cup:<s%> <S%H859>thou<s%> <S%H8551>maintainest<s%> my <S%H1486>lot.<s%>
The <S%H2256>lines<s%> are <S%H5307>fallen<s%> unto me in <S%H5273>pleasant<s%> places; <S%H637>yea,<s%> I <S%H5921>have<s%> a <S%H8231>goodly<s%> <S%H5159>heritage.<s%>

I will <S%H1288>bless<s%> <S%H853><s%> the <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> <S%H834>who<s%> hath given me <S%H3289>counsel:<s%> my <S%H3629>reins<s%> <S%H637>also<s%> <S%H3256>instruct<s%> me in the night <S%H3915>seasons.<s%>

I have <S%H7737>set<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H8548>always<s%> <S%H5048>before<s%> me: <S%H3588>because<s%> he is at my right <S%H4480>hand,<s%> <S%H3225><s%> I shall <S%H1077>not<s%> be <S%H4131>moved.<s%>

Therefore <S%H3651><s%> my <S%H3820>heart<s%> is <S%H8055>glad,<s%> and my <S%H3519>glory<s%> <S%H1523>rejoiceth:<s%> my <S%H1320>flesh<s%> <S%H637>also<s%> shall <S%H7931>rest<s%> in <S%H983>hope.<s%>

For <S%H3588><s%> thou wilt <S%H3808>not<s%> <S%H5800>leave<s%> my <S%H5315>soul<s%> in <S%H7585>hell;<s%> <S%H3808>neither<s%> wilt thou <S%H5414>suffer<s%> thine Holy <S%H2623>One<s%> to <S%H7200>see<s%> <S%H7845>corruption.<s%>

Thou wilt <S%H3045>show<s%> me the <S%H734>path<s%> of <S%H2416>life:<s%> <S%H854>in<s%> thy <S%H6440>presence<s%> is <S%H7648>fullness<s%> of <S%H8057>joy;<s%> at thy right <S%H3225>hand<s%> there are <S%H5273>pleasures<s%> <S%H5331>forevermore.<s%>
